VRef channel is 3484942336.
Temp channel is 3414425600.
18 channel is 1266941952.
19 channel is 1337458688.
VRef  is 24028.
Temp is 13102.
VRef voltage is 3327 mV.
46, and 52 are Temperature in Degree C calculated using two different formulas.

- Channels 18 and 19 are used
shell
VRef  is 9558.
Temp is 7066.
VRef voltage is 8365 mV.
140, and 170 are Temperature in Degree C calculated using two different formulas.


### issue
