**Screenshots**
If applicable, add screenshots to help explain your problem.

Comments:
[ARIOSTM - 2022-12-20T16:11:17Z]
Hi @wdfk-prog,

In order to read Temperature or Vrefint using ADC, you need to enable each channel in the ADC_CCR register.

ADC_CCR_TSEN to enable the VSENSE channel for the temperature sensor.
ADC_CCR_VREFEN to enable the Vrefint channel

When you call HAL_ADC_ConfigChannel with ADC_CHANNEL_TEMPSENSOR or ADC_CHANNEL_VREFINT the HAL driver automatically enable the corresponding channel.
The temperature sensor and vrefint are not enabled by the HAL driver when Channel 18/19 are configured.

In your test, did you make sure ADC_CCR_TSEN and ADC_CCR_VREFEN were enabled ? 

With regards,

